data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem boasts 2,259 sq ft of modern comfort. Built in 1952 but fully rebuilt to today's standards in 2016, it offers convenience and style. Enjoy an open floor plan, a sleek kitchen with soft-close cabinetry, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances. Downstairs, a guest-friendly half bath complements the inviting space. Upstairs, find four spacious bedrooms, including a primary suite with a large walk-in closet and en-suite featuring a double vanity and shower/tub combo. The upstairs laundry adds convenience, while the hall bath serves the other bedrooms. A one-car attached garage provides parking and storage. Outside, discover a charming low-maintenance front yard and backyard with full privacy fence. Patio furniture in both areas convey. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, interstates, and military bases, this home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and accessibility. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
